games.summary: Jaylen Brown scored 33 points and had 13 rebounds, Payton Pritchard added 30 points and the Boston Celtics held off the Los Angeles Clippers for a 121-118 victory on Sunday. Coming of his 82nd career triple-double with 41 points in a double-overtime victory at Dallas on Friday, James Harden scored 32 of his 37 points in the second half to lead the Clippers.
blurbs: 📋 Jordan Walsh (BOS) made just his 2nd start this season. 6 pts, 8 reb.
📋 John Collins (LAC) made just his 4th start this season. 17 pts, 2 reb.

games.summary: De’Aaron Fox had a season-high 28 points along with 11 assists and the San Antonio Spurs beat the Sacramento Kings 123-110 on Sunday with Victor Wembanyama missing his first game of the season with a calf injury. Seven players scored in double figures with Keldon Johnson contributing 14 points and 12 rebounds.
blurbs: 🆕 Luke Kornet (SA) made his first start of the season. 28 min, 13 pts.
📋 Keon Ellis (SAC) made just his 2nd start this season. 2 pts, 1 reb.

games.summary: Michael Porter Jr . scored 34 points and Tyrese Martin scored seven straight points late in the third quarter and finished with 20 as the Brooklyn Nets sent the Washington Wizards to their 11th straight loss, 129-106 Sunday night in a matchup of one-win teams.
blurbs: 📋 Egor Demin (BKN) made just his 5th start this season. 5 pts, 1 reb.

games.summary: Kevin Durant scored 35 points and Alperen Sengun had 30 points and 12 rebounds to help the Houston Rockets rally for a 117-113 overtime victory over the Orlando Magic on Sunday night. Wagner scored a season-high 29 points and Desmond Bane also set his season high with 26 points to lead the Magic on a night they were missing both Paolo Banchero and Jalen Suggs because of groin injuries.
blurbs: 📋 Tristan da Silva (ORL) made just his 2nd start this season. 13 pts, 6 reb.
📋 Anthony Black (ORL) made just his 3rd start this season. 18 pts, 3 reb.

games.summary: Moses Moody hit a career-high eight 3-pointers and scored a career-high 32 points, and the Golden State Warriors beat New Orleans 124-106 on Sunday night in what was also James Borrego's debut as Pelicans interim coach.
blurbs: 🆕 Derik Queen (NO) made his first start of the season. 25 min, 9 pts.
⬆️ Karlo Matkovic (NO) played 20 min (season avg: 10). 4 pts, 2 reb, 3 ast.
📋 Moses Moody (GS) made just his 5th start this season. 32 pts, 4 reb.
📋 Will Richard (GS) made just his 4th start this season. 9 pts, 7 reb.

games.summary: and Cooper Flagg scored 21 points apiece and teamed up on a crucial basket late in overtime to help the Dallas Mavericks to a 138-133 victory over the Portland Trail Blazers on Sunday night. Daniel Gafford added 20 points, including seven in overtime, and was one of seven Mavericks who scored in double figures.
blurbs: 📋 Brandon Williams (DAL) made just his 4th start this season. 15 pts, 3 reb.
🆕 Jerami Grant (POR) made his first start of the season. 39 min, 26 pts.

games.summary: Onyeka Okongwu had 27 points and the Atlanta Hawks overcame a 22-point deficit in the fourth quarter to stun the Phoenix Suns 124-122 on Sunday night. Atlanta’s Zaccharie Risacher scored 15 points before leaving the game in the fourth quarter after an awkward fall following a dunk.
blurbs: 📋 Onyeka Okongwu (ATL) made just his 5th start this season. 27 pts, 4 reb.

games.summary: Keyonte George made 3-pointer with 2 seconds remaining in the second overtime, Lauri Markkanen scored 47 points and the Utah Jazz beat the Chicago Bulls 150-147 on Sunday night in the NBA's highest-scoring game of the season. Coby White scored 27 points and Josh Giddey had 26 points, 12 rebounds and 13 assists for the Bulls, who have lost five straight.
blurbs: ⬆️ Jusuf Nurkic (UTAH) played 38 min (season avg: 23). 5 pts, 14 reb, 5 ast.
📋 Ace Bailey (UTAH) made just his 4th start this season. 5 pts, 1 reb.
⬆️ Brice Sensabaugh (UTAH) played 28 min (season avg: 15). 16 pts, 6 reb, 1 ast.
⬆️ Isaac Okoro (CHI) played 40 min (season avg: 25). 5 pts, 6 reb, 3 ast.
📋 Kevin Huerter (CHI) made just his 3rd start this season. 6 pts, 8 reb.
